strategy + support
"Teamwork is the ability to work together toward a common vision. The ability to direct individual accomplishments toward organizational objectives. It is the fuel that allows common people to attain uncommon results."
—Andrew Carnegie
At Badgley Phelps, we’re owned and operated by our employees, which means we’re all invested in a very personal sense in the firm’s reputation and identity. We’re not beholden to a “big guy” who dictates what we do. We’re driven by what’s best for our clients, every time. And the way that we make sure we’re providing the smartest advice to clients is by listening to and respecting one another. You might call that teamwork. We call that common sense. Good business. The right way to work. 
Sound right to you?
To explore career opportunities at Badgley Phelps, send us an email.
