            <td style="width: 200px; height: 35px; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; line-height: normal; padding: 8px; border-color: #ffffff; border-width: 2px; background-color: #dbe5f1;"><span style="font-size: 13px;">Yes</span></td>
            <td style="width: 200px; height: 35px; text-align: left; vertical-align: middle; line-height: normal; padding: 8px; border-color: #ffffff; border-width: 2px; background-color: #dbe5f1;"><span style="font-size: 13px;">Publicly disclosed financials</span></td>
