           About Edit  Established in 1966, Badgley, Phelps and Bell Investment Counsel is an independent investment management firm in Seattle. The firm manages equity, fixed-income and balanced portfolios for private and …institutional clients. An individual portfolio manager manages each portfolio at the firm and stocks are selected from an approved buy-list. The firm invests in intermediate-term bonds and each individually managed account is tailored to specific goals.more » Established in 1966, Badgley, Phelps and Bell Investment Counsel is an independent investment management firm in Seattle. The firm manages equity, fixed-income and balanced portfolios for private and institutional clients. An individual portfolio manager manages each portfolio at the firm and stocks are selected from an approved buy-list. The firm invests in intermediate-term bonds and each individually managed account is tailored to specific goals.     Is this your business? You can claim this profile as a part of the BirdEye suite. It will instantly provide you with a fully SEO optimized web presence solution and you will be able to update business information such as hours and categories, respond to reviews, share updates with followers, and so much more.   See a free demo Take BirdEye for a ride and see for yourself, instantly, how your business appears online using the Birdeye intelligence engine.              Business locations 1 location 2-9 locations 10-29 locations 30-199 locations 200+ locations Agency                           Thank you! Our reputation specialist will call you shortly to show you a personalized demo. Can't wait? Call us at 1-800-561-3357 ext. 1          Review summary      5★    4★    3★    2★    1★  1  1.0★★★★★★★★★★ 1 reviews         Things you should knowabout BirdEye    BirdEye was founded in 2012 to help businesses manage online reputation and customer experience BirdEye works with 15,000+ clients, from SMBs to large enterprises With BirdEye, you can monitor r